5-26%2Fisrael-s-ide-wins-tender-to-build-desalination-plant&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=87e71918\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-05-26/israel-s-ide-wins-tender-to-build-desalination-plant</a><br />\n<br />\nBloombergSubscribe<br />\nLi Ka-Shing Hong Kong Group Loses Israel Deal Amid U.S. Push<br />\nBy Shirley Zhao and Ivan Levingston, 26/5/2020 下午3:04:23<br />\nThe Hong Kong conglomerate founded by billionaire Li Ka-shing lost a bid for a major infrastructure project in Israel, weeks after the U.S. asked its Middle Eastern ally to review potential security threats posed by China-based companies.<br />\n<br />\nAn affiliate of CK Hutchison Holdings Ltd., the flagship of the tycoon&rsquo;s sprawling business empire, lost out on the contract to build and operate Israel&rsquo;s biggest desalination plant to IDE Technologies, a local company, the Israeli government said. In the past, Hutchison Water International Holdings Pte. had operated a desalination plant in the vicinity of the planned facility in partnership with IDE.<br />\n<br />\nIsrael&rsquo;s decision to choose a domestic bidder is the latest blow to Li&rsquo;s son and successor, CK Hutchison Chairman Victor Li, two years after his bid to buy a gas pipeline operator in Australia was blocked on national security concerns. Representatives for CK Hutchison in Hong Kong didn&rsquo;t immediately respond to requests for comment, and the U.S. Embassy in Israel had no comment."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:35:14.000Z","msg":"Iran係伊朗<br />\nIsrael係以色列"},{"pid":"19b250995c75bed7d32ae61853aa55ed01fa385b","tid":2039002,"uid":133806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b51a3cf6de4da95c0330b2623f37c19ee7133654","tid":2039002,"uid":22694,"like":160,"dislike":3,"score":157,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:31:06.000Z","msg":"伊拉克呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔係敘利亞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=